  "title": "PC 往事-1：IBM 的豪赌与 AI 时代的历史重演",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2ODkwMDI1MQ==&mid=2247485234&idx=1&sn=739ee637a71b960019e6d2ff4fc2df43",
  "date": "2025-07-31 11:04:00",
